name: Safari Themed Hand Painted False Nails! - Set Of 20
description:
This set of false nails are perfect for a  night/weekend out. Or even make fabulous presents or stocking fillers as its guaranteed that no one else will have nails like them! 


Whats included?
These false nails come in a top quality sparkly gift box, with a gift tag, professional nail glue, a nail file & instructions on how to apply. 
All together you get 22  false nails numbered 1-9 so that you can find the perfect sizes to fit your nails.
The nails are numbered on the back so that you can pair them up easy with no stress! :-)


These nails are individually hand painted piece by piece, so each design may have a slight difference.
(THE FALSE NAILS I HAVE PAINTED ON ARE NOT CHEAP AND ARE STRONG AND PROFESSIONAL AT A VERY MANAGEABLE LENGTH)


I am able to create nail designs matching near enough anything  (your favorite outfit) so if you have any design ideas please message me
